1. how to install eigen
   if you have downloaded and extracted Eigen to /home/username/eigen-eigen-5097c01bcdc4,
   then you should create a new directory outside of the Eigen root altogether. I guess something like:

   mkdir /home/username/build_eigen
   cd /home/username/build_eigen
   cmake /home/username/eigen-eigen-5097c01bcdc4
   make
   sudo make install
